"working": "\begin{align*}\log(7776) &= \log(2^5 \times 3^5) = 5\log(2) + 5\log(3)\\n\log(3) + \frac{n(n-1)}{2}\log(2) &= 5\log(2) + 5\log(3)\end{align*}",
"explanation": "Factor 7776 to simplify"
},
{
